1. *Počinjemo* vežbu u 9 sati. (We start the exercise at 9 o'clock.)
2. Već dugo *počinjemo* raditi na ovom projektu. (We have been starting to work on this project for a long time.)
3. Upravo *počinjemo* da planiramo godišnji odmor. (We are just starting to plan our annual vacation.)
4. Da li *počinjemo* sa sastankom ili čekamo još nekoga? (Do we start the meeting or wait for someone else?)
5. Kada *počinjemo* da učimo glagole? (When do we start learning verbs?)
6. *Počinjemo* sa novim kursevima sledećeg meseca. (We start with new courses next month.)
7. Ne mogu da verujem da *počinjemo* zimu, a nisam spreman za sneg. (I can't believe we're starting winter and I'm not ready for snow.)
8. *Počinjemo* da primećujemo pomake u našim marketinškim naporima. (We are starting to notice shifts in our marketing efforts.)